Steps to run
Make sure your Docker PostgreSQL container is running on port 5433:
      docker ps
Activate virtualenv:
      source /workspaces/WORKin/.venv/bin/activate
Install dependencies (if not done already):
      pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy psycopg2-binary python-dotenv
Start the backend:
      python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload
Open in browser: http://127.0.0.1:8000 → You should see:
      {"message": "Course Registration System Backend is running!"}
And in console:
      ✅ Database connection successful